data.description: MOTIVATED SELLERS!!  MODEL home for sale for the first time in Hearthstone. BRICK Ranch with basement. The FABULOUS Kitchen boasts Maple cabinets, an undermount sink and Silestone counters. HAND SCRAPED hard wood floors and Oak Trim with Solid Pine Doors throughout. The ceilings are 9ft. with CROWN MOLDING and tray ceilings in the primary bedroom and dining room. The BEAUTIFUL primary bedroom en suite has a dreamy bath with separate shower & jetted tub and it connects to an OVERSIZED walk in closet. Don't forget how many updates MODEL HOMES have. These updates include but are not limited to a TREX Deck. UPGRADED Carpeting. Ceramic in the Foyer, Kitchen, Laundry Room, and 2 Bathrooms. Designer Interior Paint was used. And additional outlets and switches were installed for electric and cable. One of the best features is the backyard-NO NEIGHBORS-you back up to a serene 40-acre wildlife refuge with pond. The LOCATION is perfect for access to expressways, shopping, restaurants and Chicago.
